## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of Alibaba's success. Some sources may lack recent updates, and the absence of direct interviews with Alibaba's leadership limits the depth of insights into internal strategies. Additionally, the report relies on secondary data, which may not fully capture the nuances of Alibaba's business operations.